      <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://res.infoq.com/news/2026/04/aws-deprecates-workmail-apprunne/en/headerimage/generatedHeaderImage-1777096878479.jpg"/><p>AWS has recently announced that WorkMail will be discontinued and that App Runner will stop accepting new customers and move into maintenance mode. Several other less popular services and features are also entering maintenance or sunset phases, triggering concern and debate across the AWS community.</p> <i>By Renato Losio</i>]]></description>
